description: Chef Delia has been delighting Detroit with delectable Mexican dishes since 1971. Everyone instantly fell in love with her flavorful family recipes - especially the original Puffy Tacos which have certainly proved to be hot stuff, as they’re being enjoyed by the thousands throughout the four El Charro locations found around town today. The cravings for this fantastic food even expanded to the streets; their loyal customers practically begged for El Charro to open up a food truck... and now here it is: big, beautiful, and fulfilling the fantasies of all the local foodies with their flavorful Mexican cuisine. Whether it’s for your next meal or next event, for all your taco needs, El Charro is top choice.
name: El Charro Food Truck
